---
import Layout from '../ui/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Sailor Success"
  description="Learn about Sailor Success - your trusted guide for Merchant Navy careers, education, and seafarer rights in India."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
      About Sailor Success
    </h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Your complete guide to joining and succeeding in the Merchant Navy.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Sailor Success provides honest, comprehensive guidance for aspiring and current merchant navy professionals. 
        We cut through the confusion and coaching institute propaganda to give you real, actionable information.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Education</strong> - DNS, GME, and maritime courses</li>
        <li><strong>Careers</strong> - Job opportunities and shipping companies</li>
        <li><strong>Finance</strong> - Salaries, taxes, and investments</li>
        <li><strong>Rights</strong> - Legal protections and seafarer welfare</li>
        <li><strong>Tools</strong> - Calculators and practical resources</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why Trust Us</h2>
      <p>
        We're built by mariners, for mariners. Our content is based on real experience, 
        regulatory documents, and actual industry practices - not sales pitches.
      </p>

      <h2>Get Started</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="/learn" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-semibold">Start learning</a> about 
        merchant navy careers, or <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-semibold">contact us</a> 
        for personalized guidance.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
